flowchart TD
    subgraph MH01_MASTER["MH-01: Master Creates Practice"]
        M1[Master opens Dashboard] --> M2[Clicks New Practice]
        M2 --> M3[Fill practice form]
        M3 --> M4{Recurring?}
        M4 -->|Yes| M5[Set recurrence rules]
        M4 -->|No| M6[Single event]
        M5 --> M7[Set capacity]
        M6 --> M7
        M7 --> M8[Set price]
        M8 --> M9[Add description + tags]
        M9 --> M10{Visibility?}
        M10 -->|Public| M11[Visible in marketplace]
        M10 -->|Private| M12[Link-only access]
        M11 --> M13[Save and Publish]
        M12 --> M13
        M13 --> M14[APScheduler creates reminder jobs]
        M14 --> M15[Practice appears in calendar]
    end
